      "sort": 600000,
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The surgeon attempts a Medicine check against the Fortitude DC of one living creature they can see within 60 feet.</p>\n<p>On a success, the surgeon's melee Strikes deal an extra [[/r {1d6}[precision]]]{1d6 precision damage} against that creature ([[/r {2d6}[precision]]]{2d6 precision damage} on a critical success) until 1 minute passes or the surgeon critically hits that creature, whichever comes first.</p>\n<p>Using this action again designates a new target and ends the effect for any previous target. A surgeon can target an individual creature no more than once per day with this ability.</p>"
        },
